fields.name: Cafe Bazaar
fields.address: Address: No 8, 2d Peyvand Alley, Farhang Sq, Sa'adat Abad, Tehran, Iran
fields.description:
“Bazaar” is a platform for the offering of Android applications and games developed by the Avayeh Hooshmand Hamrah Hezardastan company and is currently owned by the Hezardastan Technology Development Group.

Cafe Bazaar was established in January of 2011 by graduates and students of Iranian universities and has, since then, sought to provide a comprehensive platform of digital services and products to Android users with the collaboration of enthusiastic and talented Iranian developers.

fields.title: Senior Software Engineer
fields.description: The most important thing is that you are a Senior Software Engineer. You are going to have time, resources, sharp teammates and you will get proficient with our tools and technologies. So if you are good with any programming language and any technology stack, then it is the job for you.

fields.title: DevOps Engineer - TP
fields.description: The Infrastructure team’s mission is to provide building blocks for higher availability and scalability, and faster iteration in our products. As a DevOps engineer, you will research, deploy and maintain infrastructure services such as Kubernetes, Ceph, ELK, CI/CD, Prometheus, and many other tools for our product teams to build better products with ease.

fields.title: Agile People Coach
fields.description: We are seeking an experienced and highly motivated Agile Coach to join our dynamic team at Sotoon. As an Agile Coach, you will play a critical role in facilitating the adoption and implementation of the Agile mindset and Software Methodologies. You will work closely with our Product teams to facilitate and lead their tasks with your guidance and follow-up.
